<lyrics>[V1]
 1- km ạ̉nt ly mḥb rby wmạ ạ̉smạk
 ḥbk fạq dwmaⁿạ mdạy wạlạ̹drạk
 kyf ạtkẖdẖtny ạbnaⁿạ ạ̉gẖly̱ mn ạlạ̉mlạk
 wwạrtẖaⁿạ lmjd ạ̉ʿly̱ mn ạlạ̉flạk
 2- km bạṭl zmạny tḥt ạlsmạ lwlạk
 kẖlf ạlsrạb yqḍy̱ fy ạlkd wạlạ̹nhạk
 km lys fyh mʿny̱ mhmạ ḥlạ ạ̉w sẖạk
 ḥty̱ tḥl fyh bạlfyḍ mn nʿmạk
 3- tmḍy kdẖạ ạlsnyn wạlḥb ybqy̱ dẖạk
 ʿyny ạ̹lyk trnw flys ly ạ̹lạk
 ạ̉lqạk kl fjr wạ̉sẖthy rw̉yạk
 ḥty̱ yjyʾ fjr ʿyny bh tlqạk</lyrics>
<title>ʿnd ạlṣlyb</title>
</song>